#52: FILE: drivers/media/video/usbvision/usbvision-core.c:2314:
+	while ((usbvision_read_reg(usbvision, USBVISION_STATUS_REG) & 0x01) != 1);

Trailing statements (for example after any conditional) should be
on the next line.
Statements, such as::

  if (x == y) break;

should be::

  if (x == y)
          break;

